<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Oops! Something went wrong.</h1>
        <p>We're sorry, but it seems there was an error processing your request.</p>
        <p>Please try again later, or contact <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support</a> if the problem persists.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
